15 #define BYTE_SIZE_ERROR_CHECK(var_name, c_size, f_size) \
16  if(c_size != f_size) { \
17  std::stringstream err_msg; \
18  err_msg << "Size of C variable: " << c_size \
19  << " for " << var_name \
20  << " does not match size of Fortran variable: " << f_size; \
21  throw Exception(err_msg.str()); \

3440  input_exception_handling_ts_inputactions_get(const_cast<void**>(&fortran_type_c), &transfer_struct_c.ts_inputactions__f_shapes[0], &transfer_struct_c.ts_inputactions__f_len, ts_inputactions_lcl.dataFirst());
